  <resortCombinations><![CDATA[<p>There are endless combinations when it comes to multi-centre holidays in Italy. Here's a few suggestions to pair with your trip to the island of Capri. </p>
<p><strong>Sorrento</strong></p>
<p>For a multi-centre holiday, it’s easy to combine a few days on Capri with a stay in the coastal town of <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/neapolitan-riviera/sorrento">Sorrento</a>. Spend some time getting to know the city, walk amongst the ancient ruins of nearby Pompeii and taste the local olive oil grown on the terraced hills above Sorrento before hopping across the Bay of Naples by Hydrofoil. </p>
<p><strong>Naples</strong></p>
<p>Get the best of both worlds and combine your island getaway with a city break in <a data-udi="umb://document/3f78d09ffda249fe84dca900e9fedde9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f78d09ffda249fe84dca900e9fedde9}" title="Naples">Naples</a>. Uncover the cities hidden side and explore the volcanic tuffa limestone tunnels and caverns that lie 40 metres beneath the buzzing city, sample some of the country's very best coffee - with a rich espresso in one of the many local coffee shops and enjoy beautiful vistas from the <span>hilltop Castel Sant’Elmo. Combine this gritty authentic city with the picture perfect Capri as you spend your days relaxing on the sun kissed island. </span></p>
<p><strong>Ischia</strong></p>
<p>Make the most of stunning islands in the Gulf of Naples and pair your holiday to Capri with a relaxing few days on <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/neapolitan-riviera/island-of-ischia">Ischia</a>. Known for its rich thermal waters, the volcanic islands <span>curative mineral-rich spas</span> are the perfect antidote to days spent living the high life on neighboring Capri. Its just a short hop by hydrofoil or ferry from island to island. </p>
<p><strong>Amalfi Coast</strong></p>
<p>Combine your island holiday with the dramatic <a data-udi="umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47}" title="Amalfi Coast">Amallfi Coast</a>. This multi-centre, from the spectacular seascapes enjoyed from the very top of Ancapri to the winding coastal paths along the Amalfi coast, is all about the views. Enjoy the towns that cling to the cliff edge like the glamorous Possitano, Ravello with the beautiful botanical gardens of<span> Villas Cimbrone and Amalfi with its beautiful Arabic Norman Cathedral. </span></p>
<p>For more ideas and help creating or booking your perfect multi-centre holiday please call us on<span> 01483 79 11 11. </span></p>
<p> </p>]]></resortCombinations>
